Great location, especially for going to Rogers Centre, plenty of places to eat nearby, very good breakfast buffet, and has pool for the kids.	The hotel is beautifully decorated, very modern and the restaurant was great for breakfast.	Breakfast was included with the room and it is served on the second floor as a hot buffet breakfast style.	The hotel location is ideal for a visitor to the city, within easy walking distance of the entertainment district, the business district, and great shopping and dining.	The food at dinner was very good and the breakfast that was included with the room package was excellent.